    /* DESCRIPTION  :  The RQM can optionally drop PrefetchTgt requests according to the CBusy state. The RQM holds a configurable CBusy threshold and if this option is enabled by software PrefetchTgt requests are dropped by the RQM if the CBusy value is equal to or greater than the CBusy threshold
